Revision history for Perinci-AccessUtil

0.06    2015-09-06 (PERLANCAR)

	- No functional changes.

	- [dist] Move spec prereqs from RuntimeRequires to
	  DevelopRecommends to reduce deps but still allow indicating spec
	  requirement.


0.05    2014-10-24 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add option to disable encoding of result.


0.04    2014-10-23 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add function: decode_args_in_riap_req().


0.03    2014-10-23 (PERLANCAR)

	- Add function: insert_riap_stuffs_to_res.


0.02     2014-10-23 (PERLANCAR)

         - Rename module from Perinci::AccessUtil::Check to Perinci::AccessUtil.
           Rename function from check_riap_res() to
           strip_riap_stuffs_from_res().


0.01     2014-10-23 (PERLANCAR)

         - First release.
